pageContext.claim: “In Florida there is a choice between a Harvard/Yale educated man named @RonDeSantisFL who has been a great Congressman and will be a great Governor - and a Dem who is a thief and who is Mayor of poorly run Tallahassee, said to be one of the most corrupt cities in the Country!”
pageContext.analysis: Andrew Gillum, the Democratic nominee for governor in Florida, has said that an FBI investigation into Tallahassee is not looking into him. Trump claims without evidence that Gillum is a thief.
